            'Ideal for educational environments where durability and cost-effectiveness are priorities while maintaining good interactivity.',
          link: '/solutions/education',
          linkText: 'Learn more'
        },
        {
          title: 'Creative Studios',
          recommendation: 'OLED + EMR (High Precision & Color Clarity)',
